tug to attempt refloat korean bulk carrier seven tug will attempt to refloat the south korean motor bulk carrier hyundai new world tonight , lloyd ship intellig servic said in it latest updat . the vessel ground close to itaqui port in brazil last night after undock from ponta da madeira termin . lloyd said the 200,000 dwt vessel is carri about 180,000 ton of ore. five hold are partial flood and there is some leakag of bunker from doubl bottom tank . at low water tide the vessel ha a list of five degre to port and the list increas as the tide rise .